===百威法案===
鉴于发生过众多在体育馆内致人死亡案件，巴西2003年通过一项禁止在体育场馆内销售酒精。由于[[百威|百威]]自1986年是世界杯的“官方指定啤酒”，国际足联要求巴西允许在世界杯期间销售酒精。为此，巴西通过一项铺平世界杯期间酒类销售道路的法案，绰号“百威法案<ref>[http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2012/03/07/148155110/brazil-moves-to-ease-soccer-beer-ban-as-world-cup-spat-with-fifa-grows Brazil Moves To Ease Soccer Beer Ban, As World Cup Spat With FIFA Grows] {{Wayback|url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2012/03/07/148155110/brazil-moves-to-ease-soccer-beer-ban-as-world-cup-spat-with-fifa-grows |date=20140717022754 }}, ''[[NPR|NPR]]'' (7 March 2012)</ref><ref>[http://en.mercopress.com/2012/05/10/brazilian-senate-approves-budweiser-bill-ending-dispute-with-fifa-over-world-cup-sponsoring Brazilian Senate approves ‘Budweiser bill’ ending dispute with FIFA over World Cup sponsoring] {{Wayback|url=http://en.mercopress.com/2012/05/10/brazilian-senate-approves-budweiser-bill-ending-dispute-with-fifa-over-world-cup-sponsoring |date=20140714230247 }}, ''Merco Press'', (10 May 2012)</ref>”。

===抽签争议===
[[2014年世界杯足球赛抽签|抽签]]时，国际足联决定第二档的欧洲球队随机抽签，引发争议。此前彩排时，排名最后的欧洲球队被抽至该档<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/05/upshot/the-world-cup-draw-is-unfair-heres-a-better-way.html|title=The World Cup Draw Is Unfair. Here’s a Better Way.|publisher=The New York Times|date=2014-06-04|accessdate=2014-06-06|archive-date=2014-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605212704/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/05/upshot/the-world-cup-draw-is-unfair-heres-a-better-way.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这样，法国逃避抽签的艰难，[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週D组|落到了意大利头上]]。

许多官员、球迷和记者抱怨，指出身为法国人的国际足联秘书长瓦尔克提议修改规则，还怀疑另一名影响的法国人——欧洲足联主席[[米歇尔·普拉蒂尼|米歇尔·普拉蒂尼]]协助批准。

翌日，意大利体育报刊《[[罗马体育报|罗马体育报]]》刊登头条：《2014年世界杯抽签：何为丑闻？》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.corrieredellosport.it/calcio/opinioni/2013/12/07-343508/Sorteggi+Mondiali+2014%2C+che+scandalo%21|title=Sorteggi Mondiali 2014, che scandalo!|publisher=Corriere dello Sport|date=2013-12-07|accessdate=2014-07-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714162602/http://www.corrieredellosport.it/calcio/opinioni/2013/12/07-343508/Sorteggi+Mondiali+2014,+che+scandalo!|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>。

==小组赛==
===巴西 v. 克罗地亚===
日本裁判[[西村雄一|西村雄一]]，因在{{nft|巴西}}对阵{{nft|克罗地亚}}的[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週A组|A组揭幕战]]中，作出若干偏向东道主的判罚，而面临严厉批评。

第71分钟，克罗地亚后卫[[德扬·洛夫伦|-{zh-hans:德扬·洛夫伦; zh-hk:迪贊·洛夫雲;}-]]禁区盯防时，将手伸向[[佛雷德里科·查韦斯·格德斯|-{zh-hans:弗雷德;zh-hk:費特;zh-tw:佛雷德;}-]]手臂下方致使其倒地。西村判罚巴西[[点球|点球]]，[[内马尔|内马尔]]打入第二个进球，比分定局3-1，巴西获胜。这一判罚遭到各方面的谴责，包括前国际足联顶级裁判<ref name="Goal Meier">{{cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/3841/world-cup-2014/2014/06/13/4879134/fred-should-have-been-booked-for-diving-brazil-blunder-ref-comes- |title='Fred should have been booked for diving' - Brazil blunder ref comes under fire |work=[[Goal.com|Goal.com]] |last=Voakes |first=Kris |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616050805/http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/3841/world-cup-2014/2014/06/13/4879134/fred-should-have-been-booked-for-diving-brazil-blunder-ref-comes- |dead-url=no }}</ref>、报纸专栏作家<ref name="The Globe and Mail Brazil Croatia">{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/soccer/world-cup/kelly-a-referee-undone-by-the-pressure-in-brazil/article19149880/ |title=Kelly: A referee undone by the pressure in Brazil |work=[[环球邮报|环球邮报]] |last=Paulo |first=Sao |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081754/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/soccer/world-cup/kelly-a-referee-undone-by-the-pressure-in-brazil/article19149880/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Daily Mail Brazil Croatia">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2656584/Brazil-2-1-Croatia-Neymar-scores-twice-escapes-sending-hosts-start-win-Sao-Paulo.html |title=Brazil 3-1 Croatia: Neymar scores twice (and escapes a sending off) as Oscar stunner rounds off opening win for hosts |work=[[每日邮报|每日邮报]] |last=Samuel |first=Martin |date=2014-06-12 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613123503/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2656584/Brazil-2-1-Croatia-Neymar-scores-twice-escapes-sending-hosts-start-win-Sao-Paulo.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CNN Almasy">{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/12/sport/football/world-cup-five-more-things/index.html |title=Five memorable moments from the World Cup |work=[[CNN|CNN]] |last=Almasy |first=Steve |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714175018/http://edition.cnn.com/2014/06/12/sport/football/world-cup-five-more-things/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和其他队球员<ref name="AP Remy">{{cite news |url=http://tbo.com/ap/sports/remy-brazils-fred-should-be-punished-for-penalty-ap_sports054a0dfd6cb74da388d2d15989f3a999 |title=Remy: Brazil's Fred should be punished for penalty |newspaper=The Tampa Tribune |agency=Associated Press |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140702111251/http://tbo.com/ap/sports/remy-brazils-fred-should-be-punished-for-penalty-ap_sports054a0dfd6cb74da388d2d15989f3a999 |archivedate=2014-07-02 }}</ref>，甚至有西村祖国的球迷称-{zh-hans:洛夫伦; zh-hk:洛夫雲;}-的接触很微，-{zh-hans:弗雷德;zh-hk:費特;zh-tw:佛雷德;}-是[[假摔|自己倒地]]的<ref name="Japanese fans regret and 26th minute">{{cite news |url=http://tbo.com/ap/sports/japanese-fans-express-regret-over-nishimuras-call-ap_sportsacc2edcfdaa1487e8ac8f21b7c0e2901 |title=Japanese fans express regret over Nishimura's call |newspaper=The Tampa Tribune |agency=Associated Press |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140702111252/http://tbo.com/ap/sports/japanese-fans-express-regret-over-nishimuras-call-ap_sportsacc2edcfdaa1487e8ac8f21b7c0e2901 |archivedate=2014-07-02 }}</ref>。12分钟后，巴西门将[[朱利奥·塞萨尔|-{zh-hans:朱利奥·塞萨尔;zh-hk:祖利奧·施薩;zh-tw:儒利奧·塞薩爾;}-]]接高空坠落的球时，克罗地亚前锋[[伊维卡·奥利奇|-{zh-hans:伊维卡·奥利奇;zh-hk:伊維卡·奧歷;zh-tw:伊維卡·奧利奇;}-]]被吹犯规，同样存在争议而遭到多方谴责<ref name="The Guardian live Brazil Croatia">{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/12/brazil-v-croatia-world-cup-2014-live-report |title=Brazil 3-1 Croatia: World Cup 2014 – as it happened |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |last=Glendenning |first=Barry |date=2014-06-12 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615091338/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/12/brazil-v-croatia-world-cup-2014-live-report |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Eurosport 1 Brazil Croatia">{{cite web |url=https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/blogs/desmond-kane/forget-neymar-brazil-national-hero-yuichi-nishimura-225207798.html |title=Forget Neymar, Brazil’s new national hero is Yuichi Nishimura |work=[[Eurosport|Eurosport]] |last=Kane |first=Desmond |date=2014-06-12 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613185312/https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/blogs/desmond-kane/forget-neymar-brazil-national-hero-yuichi-nishimura-225207798.html |archivedate=2014-06-13 }}</ref><ref name="Goal summary Brazil Croatia">{{cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/match/brazil-vs-croatia/1220070/report |title=Brazil 3 - 1 Croatia Match report - Goal.com |work=[[Goal.com|Goal.com]] |date=2014-06-12 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615160852/http://www.goal.com/en-gb/match/brazil-vs-croatia/1220070/report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

