te=2014-06-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613182458/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/worldcup/brazil-3-croatia-1-fifa-defend-underfire-referee-yuichi-nishimura-as-japanese-official-caught-up-in-diving-row-during-opening-world-cup-match-9535713.html |archivedate=2014-06-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。国际足联市场总监蒂埃利·韦尔，拒绝就西村青睐巴西作答<ref name="Busacca Weil Daily Mail" />。

===墨西哥 v. 喀麦隆：-{zh-hans:吉奥瓦尼;zh-hk:基奧雲尼;zh-tw:吉奧瓦尼;}-的两粒进球无效===
{{nft|墨西哥}}对阵{{nft|喀麦隆}}的[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週A组#墨西哥_v_喀麦隆|A组比赛]]中，墨西哥[[吉奥瓦尼·多斯桑托斯|-{zh-hans:吉奥瓦尼·多斯桑托斯;zh-hk:基奧雲尼·杜斯山度士;zh-tw:吉奧瓦尼·多斯桑托斯;}-]]两粒进球，被错误判罚为[[越位|越位]]。慢镜头显示，他与后卫并行在先，喀麦隆球员传球在后<ref>{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/06/13/world-cup-2014-mexicos-giovani-dos-santos-has-two-goals-wrongly-ruled-out-for-offside-in-first-half-against-cameroon-4760966/ |title=World Cup 2014: Mexico’s Giovani Dos Santos has TWO goals WRONGLY ruled out for offside in first-half against Cameroon |work=Metro (British newspaper) |last=Duncan |first=Hannah |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140616045953/http://metro.co.uk/2014/06/13/world-cup-2014-mexicos-giovani-dos-santos-has-two-goals-wrongly-ruled-out-for-offside-in-first-half-against-cameroon-4760966/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最终墨西哥1-0获胜。《[[卫报|卫报]]》的艾米·劳伦斯称“杯赛裁判不称职”，呼吁国际足联主席[[塞普·布拉特|塞普·布拉特]]，让领队拿回放录像驳斥每场比赛的两个决议，该可能性被布拉特在赛前讨论<ref name="The Guardian Amy Lawrence Mexico Cameroon">{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2014/jun/13/mexico-cameroon-disallowed-goals-referees-controversy-world-cup |title=Mexico’s disallowed goals add to World Cup’s incompetent officiating |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |last=Lawrence |first=Amy |date=2014-06-13 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615130339/http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2014/jun/13/mexico-cameroon-disallowed-goals-referees-controversy-world-cup |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="The Guardian Sepp Blatter video review">{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/11/sepp-blatter-video-challenge-managers-fifa |title=Sepp Blatter does U-turn over allowing video challenges in live play |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |last=Gibson |first=Owen |date=2014-06-11 |accessdate=2014-06-16 |archive-date=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615091244/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/11/sepp-blatter-video-challenge-managers-fifa |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年6月20日，国际足联宣布，取消事件负责人，哥伦比亚边裁翁贝托·克拉维霍进一步执法赛事的资格<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/06/20/uk-soccer-world-linesman-idUKKBN0EV1TI20140620|title=FIFA drops linesman who ruled out Mexico 'goals'|date=2014-06-20|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-date=2014-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140720202441/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/06/20/uk-soccer-world-linesman-idUKKBN0EV1TI20140620|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===西班牙 v. 荷兰：迭戈·科斯塔的行为===
{{nft|西班牙}}的巴西籍前锋[[迭戈·科斯塔|迭戈·科斯塔]]，无疑是比赛备受瞩目的焦点。科斯塔回到家乡首次参加世界杯，但他的新球队却以5-1在[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週B组#西班牙_v._荷兰|B组比赛]]中输给{{nft|荷兰}}，全场比赛遭到当地球迷的嘲笑和侮辱。科斯塔在比赛中，明显地用头顶撞对手[[布鲁诺·马丁斯·因迪|-{zh-hans:马丁斯·因迪;zh-hk:馬田斯·恩迪}-]]，随后被主帅[[比森特·德尔·博斯克|比森特·德尔·博斯克]]用前锋[[费尔南多·托雷斯|费尔南多·托雷斯]]换下<ref>{{cite news|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/sports/football/fifa-world-cup-diego-costas-brazil-debut-for-spain-marred-by-defeat-and-humiliation/|title=FIFA World Cup: Diego Costa's Brazil debut for Spain marred by defeat and humiliation|date=2014-06-14|accessdate=2014-06-14|archive-date=2014-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614213448/http://indianexpress.com/article/sports/football/fifa-world-cup-diego-costas-brazil-debut-for-spain-marred-by-defeat-and-humiliation/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://sg.sports.yahoo.com/news/worth-time-diego-costa-step-spain-093000963.html|title=Was he worth it? Time for Diego Costa to step up for Spain|date=2014-06-18|accessdate=2014-06-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714150138/https://sg.sports.yahoo.com/news/worth-time-diego-costa-step-spain-093000963.html|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>。

===德国 v. 葡萄牙===
