isher=IOL.co.za |date= |accessdate=2014-06-18 |archive-date=2014-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618075652/http://www.iol.co.za/sport/soccer/cup-competitions/portugal-coach-cries-foul-1.1704133 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的马克·奥戈登将其标签为“本届世界杯可疑判罚的又一例子，轻微接触不足以阻挡最被人质疑的-{zh-cn:格策; zh-hk:葛斯; zh-tw:格策}-<ref>{{cite news|first=Mark|last=Ogden|title=Germany v Portugal: Thomas Müller scores hat-trick after Portuguese capitulate following straight red card for Pepe|date=2014-06-16|publisher=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10904100/Germany-v-Portugal-Thomas-Muller-scores-hat-trick-after-Portuguese-capitulate-following-straight-red-card-for-Pepe.html|accessdate=2014-06-22|archive-date=2014-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621223827/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10904100/Germany-v-Portugal-Thomas-Muller-scores-hat-trick-after-Portuguese-capitulate-following-straight-red-card-for-Pepe.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

