.com.pt/alemanha-portugal-hecatombe-em-direto/ |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref>。赛后采访时，-{zh-hans:本托;zh-hk:賓圖;zh-tw:本托;}-表示两次判罚表明有“偏见”，并称：“我不能把罪责扔给裁判，我们也有过错，但是上半场发生的情况，让我们接下来陷入僵局……球员被迫罚出场。我不知道这是不是佩佩的声誉带来。这取决你们赋予佩佩的名声<ref>{{cite news|last1=Wilson|first1=Paul|title=Portugal's Paulo Bento accuses referee of bias after rout by Germany|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/16/portugal-paulo-bento-germany-world-cup|accessdate=2014-07-03|publisher=[[卫报|卫报]]|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714131945/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/16/portugal-paulo-bento-germany-world-cup|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

===意大利 v. 哥斯达黎加：基耶利尼踢翻-{zh-hans:坎贝尔; zh-hk:甘保; zh-tw:坎貝爾;}-===
