{{nft|阿根廷}}对阵{{nft|伊朗}}的[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週F组#阿根廷_v_伊朗|F组比赛]]中，塞尔维亚籍裁判[[米洛拉德·马哲|米洛拉德·马哲]]未判罚伊朗队[[任意球|任意球]]，伊朗队员怒火中烧<ref name="metro-2014">{{cite news|first=|last=|title=Should Iran have had a penalty for Pablo Zabaleta’s foul on Ashkan Dejagah in the box?|date=2014-06-21|publisher=Metro (British newspaper)|url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/06/21/should-iran-have-had-a-penalty-for-pablo-zabaletas-foul-on-ashkan-dejagah-in-the-box-4770930/|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2014-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624011805/http://metro.co.uk/2014/06/21/should-iran-have-had-a-penalty-for-pablo-zabaletas-foul-on-ashkan-dejagah-in-the-box-4770930/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而推搡裁判<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://playtheadvantage.com/2014/06/21/thoughts-on-the-referees-day-ten/ |title=Thoughts on the Referees: Day Ten: Milorad Mazic (SRB), Argentina v. Iran |accessdate=2014-08-12 |archive-date=2014-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140823052503/http://playtheadvantage.com/2014/06/21/thoughts-on-the-referees-day-ten/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第55分钟，伊朗中场[[阿什坎·德贾加|-{zh-hans:阿什坎·德贾加;zh-hk:阿殊汗·迪查加;zh-tw:阿什坎·德賈加;}-]]禁区内被阿根廷后卫[[柏保路·薩巴列達|-{zh-hans:巴勃罗·萨瓦莱塔;zh-hk:柏保路·薩巴列達;zh-tw:巴勃羅·薩瓦萊塔;}-]]侵犯，裁判未判罚任意球，赛后引发就该行为是否属于犯规的讨论。Jam-e-jam、Quds和Iran等伊朗平面媒体，将没有判罚点球的马哲骂了个狗血淋头，称他帮助阿根廷赢得比赛<ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|title=Iran media lament 'injustice' after Argentina World Cup meet|date=2014-06-22|publisher=The Financial Express (India)|url=http://www.financialexpress.com/news/iran-media-lament-injustice-after-argentina-world-cup-meet/1263157|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714140808/http://www.financialexpress.com/news/iran-media-lament-injustice-after-argentina-world-cup-meet/1263157|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Pravda.ru的蒂莫西·班克罗夫特称马哲“带偏见且不称职”，他在第55分钟的判罚，决定了“裁判选择的质量，主宰了国际足联世界杯比赛的恶心评论<ref>{{cite news|first=Timothy|last=Bancroft-Hinchey|title=Iran media lament 'injustice' after Argentina World Cup meet|date=2014-06-21|publisher=Pravda.ru|url=http://english.pravda.ru/news/sports/21-06-2014/127856-iran_argentina-0/#.U6fBkkBPg_d|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2014-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140623230031/http://english.pravda.ru/news/sports/21-06-2014/127856-iran_argentina-0/#.U6fBkkBPg_d|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。《新城报》写道，尽管-{zh-hans:萨瓦莱塔;zh-hk:薩巴列達;zh-tw:薩瓦萊塔;}-抢球时绊倒了-{zh-hans:德贾加;zh-hk:迪查加;zh-tw:德賈加;}-，“回放显示，伊朗队应该获得点球<ref name="metro-2014"/>”。《[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]》的马特·劳顿<ref>{{cite news|first=Matt|last=Lawton|title=Argentina 1-0 Iran: Lionel Messi magic saves Alejandro Sabella as superstar fires home injury-time stunner to break minnows and reach last 16|date=2014-06-21|publisher=[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2664569/Argentina-1-0-Iran-Lionel-Messi-rescue-minute-stunner-Ashkan-Dejagah-scare.html|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622213902/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2664569/Argentina-1-0-Iran-Lionel-Messi-rescue-minute-stunner-Ashkan-Dejagah-scare.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[体坛博客联盟|体坛博客联盟]]的凯文·麦考利<ref>{{cite news|first=Barney|last=Ronay|title=Argentina through after Lionel Messi breaks battling Iran at the last|date=2014-06-21|publisher=[[卫报|卫报]]|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/21/argentina-iran-world-cup-2014-group-f-match-report|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622204509/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/21/argentina-iran-world-cup-2014-group-f-match-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>认为-{zh-hans:德贾加;zh-hk:迪查加;zh-tw:德賈加;}-“强力要求点球”。然而，《[[卫报|卫报]]》的巴尼·罗纳和[[美联社|美联社]]的卡尔·里特尔<ref name="ritter-ap-2014">{{cite news|first=Karl|last=Ritter|title=Iran Coach Blasts Referee Who Waved Away Penalty|date=2014-06-21|publisher=[[美联社|美联社]]|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/iran-coach-blasts-referee-waving-penalty-24247756|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140622163015/http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/iran-coach-blasts-referee-waving-penalty-24247756|dead-url=no}}</ref>，却在报道中写道电视回放显示，-{zh-hans:萨瓦莱塔;zh-hk:薩巴列達;zh-tw:薩瓦萊塔;}-先碰到球，-{zh-hans:德贾加;zh-hk:迪查加;zh-tw:德賈加;}-然后倒下，阿根廷不算犯规。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》亦认同判罚：“-{zh-hans:德贾加;zh-hk:迪查加;zh-tw:德賈加;}-嚷着要点球，几乎粗暴对待无奈的裁判，我不知道这是为何，但回放显示-{zh-hans:萨瓦莱塔;zh-hk:薩巴列達;zh-tw:薩瓦萊塔;}-赢得球，尽管有些笨拙<ref>{{cite web|last1=Smyth|first1=Rob|title=Argentina v Iran, World Cup 2014: live|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10916423/Argentina-vs-Iran-World-Cup-2014-live.html|publisher=每日电讯报|accessdate=2014-06-28|archive-date=2014-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624020451/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10916423/Argentina-vs-Iran-World-Cup-2014-live.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

伊朗队主帅[[卡路士·昆洛斯|-{zh-hans:卡洛斯·奎罗斯;zh-hk:卡路士·昆洛斯;zh-tw:卡洛斯·凱羅斯;}-]]在赛后质疑第55分钟的错误判罚：“这应该是点球加红牌，没有借口可言。有理由能解释塞尔维亚裁判没有给出点球吗？这家伙今晚，乃至余生怎能安睡？总而言之，我想一对一地跟他交谈。他凭什么这样对待我们<ref name="ritter-ap-2014"/>？”阿根廷主帅[[亚历杭德罗·萨贝拉|亚历杭德罗·萨贝拉]]支持马哲的判罚，觉得-{zh-hans:萨瓦莱塔;zh-hk:薩巴列達;zh-tw:薩瓦萊塔;}-先拿到球<ref>{{cite news|first=Andy|last=Mitten|title=Queiroz slams ref after Argentina loss|date=2014-06-21|publisher=[[ESPN_FC|ESPN FC]]|url=http://www.espnfc.com/fifa-world-cup/story/1900202/carlos-queiroz-criticises-referee-milorad-mazic-after-iran-defeat-to-argentina|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2014-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140625025233/http://www.espnfc.com/fifa-world-cup/story/1900202/carlos-queiroz-criticises-referee-milorad-mazic-after-iran-defeat-to-argentina|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ritter-ap-2014"/>。

