苏亚雷斯此前曾两次咬对手：2010年咬了[[奥特曼·巴卡尔|奥特曼·巴卡尔]]而禁赛七场<ref>{{cite web |url=http://english.ajax.nl/News/Archive/Article/Ajax-accepts-Suarez-suspension.htm |title=Ajax accepts Suarez’ suspension |work=Ajax.nl |publisher=AFC Ajax |date=2010-11-24 |accessdate=2011-08-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120407013208/http://english.ajax.nl/News/Archive/Article/Ajax-accepts-Suarez-suspension.htm |archivedate=2012-04-07 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/nov/22/luis-suarez-biting-otman-bakkal |title=Luis Suárez: 'The Cannibal of Ajax'? |work=The Guardian |agency=Associated Press |date=2010-11-22 |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-date=2011-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111202032846/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2010/nov/22/luis-suarez-biting-otman-bakkal |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/clubfootball/news/newsid=1340434.html |title=Suarez banned for seven games |agency=Press Association |work=FIFA.com |date=2010-11-24 |accessdate=2011-02-02 |archive-date=2011-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110120003853/http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/clubfootball/news/newsid=1340434.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2013年咬了[[布拉尼斯拉夫·伊雲奴域|布拉尼斯拉夫·-{zh-hans:伊万诺维奇;zh-hk:伊雲奴域;zh-tw:伊凡諾維奇;}-]]而禁赛十场<ref>{{cite news |last=Fifield |first=Dominic |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/blog/2013/apr/21/luis-suarez-bite |title=Luis Suárez's bite has proven again he is a liability, even at his peak |work=The Guardian |date=2013-04-21 |accessdate=2013-04-21 |archive-date=2013-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130422043711/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/blog/2013/apr/21/luis-suarez-bite |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=David Cameron calls on FA to take hard line with Luis Suárez over bite |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2013/apr/22/luis-suarez-charged-biting-ivanovic |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |accessdate=2013-06-07 |first=Andy |last=Hunter |date=2013-04-22 |archive-date=2013-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624220739/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2013/apr/22/luis-suarez-charged-biting-ivanovic |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Hunter |first=Andy |title=Luis Suárez says three-match ban is enough for biting Branislav Ivanovic |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2013/apr/23/luis-suarez-liverpool-fa-bite |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |accessdate=2013-06-07 |date=2013-04-23 |archive-date=2013-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430225422/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2013/apr/23/luis-suarez-liverpool-fa-bite |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因被批没有意识到“严重性”。

2014年6月26日，国际足联纪律委员会禁止苏亚雷斯参加九场国际比赛，判决立即生效，这意味着苏亚雷斯无法继续参加世界杯，也是世界杯历史上最严重的禁令，超越了因在[[1994年世界杯足球赛|1994年世界杯]]咬了[[路易斯·恩里克|路易斯·恩里克]]而被禁赛八场的[[毛罗·塔索蒂|毛罗·-{zh-hans:塔索蒂;zh-hk:泰索迪;zh-tw:塔索蒂;}-]]<ref name="Ban2014">{{cite news |last=De Menezes |first=Jack |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/worldcup/luis-suarez-banned-fifa-hand-striker-record-ninegame-ban-and-a-four-month-football-ban-for-biting-giorgio-chiellini-in-biggest-ever-world-cup-suspension-9565686.html |title=Luis Suarez banned: Fifa hand striker record nine-game ban AND a four month football ban for biting Giorgio Chiellini in biggest ever World Cup suspension |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2014-06-26 |publisher=The Independent |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185017/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/worldcup/luis-suarez-banned-fifa-hand-striker-record-ninegame-ban-and-a-four-month-football-ban-for-biting-giorgio-chiellini-in-biggest-ever-world-cup-suspension-9565686.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Luis Suarez suspended">{{cite news|title=Luis Suárez banned for four months for biting in World Cup game|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/26/world-cup-luis-suarez-ban-biting-uruguay|accessdate=2014-06-26|publisher=The Guardian|date=2014-06-26|archive-date=2014-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706152415/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/26/world-cup-luis-suarez-ban-biting-uruguay|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/2014-world-cup-fifa-bans-suarez-games-months/story?id=24314667|title=FIFA Suspends and Fines Suarez for 9 Games and 4 Months After Biting Player|publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|date=2014-06-26|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715203607/http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/2014-world-cup-fifa-bans-suarez-games-months/story?id=24314667|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还被禁止参与足球活动四个月，并处以10万[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]（约合65700英镑/82000欧元/119000美元）<ref name="Suarez suspension FIFA">{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=6/news=luis-suarez-suspended-for-nine-matches-and-banned-for-four-months-from-2386354.html |title=Luis Suárez suspended for nine matches and banned for four months from any football-related activity |publisher=[[FIFA|FIFA]] |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703172739/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y%3D2014/m%3D6/news%3Dluis-suarez-suspended-for-nine-matches-and-banned-for-four-months-from-2386354.html |archivedate=2014-07-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Ban2014"/><ref name="Luis Suarez suspended"/>。判罚的严重基于苏亚雷斯第三次在进攻中咬人，缺乏反省<ref name="lostbalance">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/28/luis-suarez-bite-balance-hit-face-chiellini|title=Luis Suárez bite defence: I lost balance and hit my teeth against Chiellini|last=Gibson|first=Owen|date=28 June 2014|work=The Observer|accessdate=29 June 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711010720/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/28/luis-suarez-bite-balance-hit-face-chiellini|archivedate=2014-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。苏亚雷斯被禁赛，也导致乌拉圭在[[2014年世界杯足球赛淘汰赛阶段|下一场比赛中]]以0-2输给[[哥伦比亚国家足球队|哥伦比亚]]而离开世界杯<ref>{{cite web|title=James Rodriguez scores twice, lifts Colombia to first quarterfinal|url=http://www.si.com/planet-futbol/2014/06/28/colombia-uruguay-world-cup-commentary-recap-knockout-stage|publisher=Associated Press|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714120232/http://www.si.com/planet-futbol/2014/06/28/colombia-uruguay-world-cup-commentary-recap-knockout-stage|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[乌拉圭足球协会|乌拉圭足球协会]]在禁令被宣布的同一天提出上诉<ref name="Uruguay to appeal Suarez ban for biting">{{cite news|title=Uruguay to appeal Suarez ban for biting|url=http://www.dw.de/uruguay-to-appeal-suarez-ban-for-biting/a-17739744|accessdate=2014-06-26|publisher=Deutsche Welle|date=2014-06-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627111401/http://www.dw.de/uruguay-to-appeal-suarez-ban-for-biting/a-17739744|archivedate=2014-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。苏亚雷斯的律师表示：“我们没有怀疑”任何的欧洲比赛抵抗苏亚雷斯<ref>{{cite web|title=Luis Suarez: Uruguay captain Lugano dismisses 'bite' claims|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28026610|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2014-06-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705044030/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28026610|archivedate=2014-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。乌拉圭人对苏亚雷斯各种辩护，质疑他是否真的咬了基耶利尼，批评禁令过于严重。乌拉圭总统[[何塞·穆希卡|何塞·穆希卡]]将禁令视为“[[法西斯主义|法西斯主义]]”，称国际足联官员是一班“婊子的臭王八蛋<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/26/us-soccer-world-suarez-president-idUSKBN0F101O20140626|title=Leave Suarez alone, Uruguay president urges|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2014-06-29|last=Schreiber|first=Irene|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626073010/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/26/us-soccer-world-suarez-president-idUSKBN0F101O20140626|archivedate=2014-06-26|accessdate=2014-07-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Luis Suarez bite ban: Uruguay President Jose Mujica insults Fifa|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28085880|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2014-06-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701131027/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28085880|archivedate=2014-07-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。乌足联主席威尔马·巴尔德斯<ref name="Uruguay to appeal Suarez ban for biting"/> 、乌拉圭队长[[迭戈·卢加诺|-{zh-hans:迭戈·卢加诺;zh-hk:迪亞高·盧根奴;zh-tw:迪亞哥·盧加諾;}-]]<ref>{{cite web|title=World Cup 2014: How Uruguay closed ranks over Luis Suarez|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28029656|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2014-06-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710134942/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28029656|archivedate=2014-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>、乌拉圭主帅[[奥斯卡·塔巴雷斯|奥斯卡·塔巴雷斯]]以辞去国际足联职位的方式，对禁令表示抗议<ref name="reactions">{{cite web|title=Luis Suarez: Uruguay coach Oscar Tabarez to quit Fifa posts|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28058345|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2014-06-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630080740/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28058345|archivedate=2014-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。乌拉圭媒体亦产生挑衅和抵触情绪<ref>{{cite web|title=Luis Suarez: global scrutiny after Giorgio Chiellini 'bite'|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28015683|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2014-06-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626212347/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28015683|archivedate=2014-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。被咬的基耶利尼也认为禁令过分，而[[国际职业足球员协会|国际职业足球员协会]]为呼吁“他所需的支持”，认为“重点应放在苏亚雷斯的康复和认真治疗”上<ref name="reactions"/>。

事件发生六天后的6月30日，苏亚雷斯透过[[Twitter|Twitter]]向基耶利尼道歉，称咬人是与基耶利尼发生碰撞的结果，发誓不再有同类事件发生<ref name="Suarez apology Twitter">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/luis16suarez/status/483659463417548800 |title=Suárez's official apology |publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]] |author=[[路爾斯·艾拔圖·蘇亞雷斯|路易斯·苏亚雷斯]] |date=2014-06-30 |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701015706/https://twitter.com/luis16suarez/status/483659463417548800 |archivedate=2014-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Suarez apology The Guardian">{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/30/luis-suarez-apologises-giorgio-chiellini-bite |title=Luis Suárez apologises to Giorgio Chiellini for World Cup bite |newspaper=The Guardian |last=Lucas |first=Dan |date=30 June 2014 |accessdate=30 June 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707180448/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/30/luis-suarez-apologises-giorgio-chiellini-bite |archivedate=2014-07-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。基耶利尼则回复自己已忘掉了事件，希望国际足联减少对苏亚雷斯的禁赛<ref name="Chiellini response Twitter">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/chiellini/status/483671807380443136 |title=Chiellini's Twitter response |publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]] |author=[[基耶利尼|基耶利尼]] |date=2014-06-30 |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701235301/https://twitter.com/chiellini/status/483671807380443136 |archivedate=2014-07-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Suarez apology The Guardian"/>。

7月3日，乌足联正式就苏亚雷斯的禁令提出上诉<ref name="AUF appeal">{{cite news |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/12040/9370577/world-cup-uruguay-launch-suarez-appeal |title=World Cup: FIFA confirm Uruguay have appealed against Luis Suarez’s biting ban |publisher=[[Sky_Sports|Sky Sports]] |date=2014-07-03 |accessdate=2014-07-03 |archive-date=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708032656/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/12040/9370577/world-cup-uruguay-launch-suarez-appeal |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Suarez suspended while appeal is pending">{{cite news |url=http://www.courant.com/sports/world-cup/hc-luis-suarez-suspended-0627-20140626,0,2075182.story |title=Luis Suarez's Bite Results In Nine-Match Ban; Uruguay Will Appeal |newspaper=Hartford Courant |agency=[[路透社|路透社]] |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2014-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707191830/http://www.courant.com/sports/world-cup/hc-luis-suarez-suspended-0627-20140626%2C0%2C2075182.story |archivedate=2014-07-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但7月10日被国际足联驳回<ref name="Suarez appeal rejected FIFA">{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y=2014/m=7/news=appeals-of-suarez-and-the-uruguayan-fa-rejected-sanctions-upheld-2403024.html |title=Appeals of Suarez and the Uruguayan FA rejected, sanctions upheld |publisher=[[FIFA|FIFA]] |date=2014-07-10 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711041429/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/news/y%3D2014/m%3D7/news%3Dappeals-of-suarez-and-the-uruguayan-fa-rejected-sanctions-upheld-2403024.html |archivedate=2014-07-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Suarez appeal rejected BBC">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28251964 |title=Luis Suarez's appeal against bite ban rejected by Fifa |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2014-07-10 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711042532/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28251964 |archivedate=2014-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Suarez appeal rejected Sky Sports">{{cite web |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/12040/9378008/fifa-rejects-luis-suarez-appeal-against-ban-for-biting-giorgio-chiellini |title=FIFA rejects Luis Suarez appeal against ban for biting Giorgio Chiellini |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2014-07-10 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |archive-date=2014-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713011724/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/12040/9378008/fifa-rejects-luis-suarez-appeal-against-ban-for-biting-giorgio-chiellini |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但禁令没能阻止苏亚雷斯转会到另一家足球俱乐部<ref name="Suarez no transfer ban">{{cite web |url=http://www.itv.com/worldcup/liverpool-keep-counsel-over-suarez-ban-reaction |title=Liverpool keep counsel over Suarez ban reaction |work=ITV News |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2014-06-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626233554/http://www.itv.com/worldcup/liverpool-keep-counsel-over-suarez-ban-reaction |archivedate=2014-06-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，苏亚雷斯7月11日宣布转会到[[巴塞罗那竞技俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Luis Suarez: Liverpool & Barcelona agree deal for striker|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28180600|accessdate=2014-07-11|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2014-07-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712035115/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28180600|archivedate=2014-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[转会_(足球)|转会]]前一天，苏亚雷斯的道歉受到巴萨人的赞赏：巴塞罗那主席何塞普·玛丽亚·巴托梅称道歉是种“光荣”；体育总监[[安多尼·苏维萨雷塔|安多尼·苏维萨雷塔]]对苏亚雷斯以“足够的谦卑承认错误”表示欢迎；新加盟的[[伊万·拉基蒂奇|-{zh-hans:伊万·拉基蒂奇;zh-hk:艾雲·拿傑迪錫;zh-tw:伊萬·拉基蒂奇;}-]]赞赏苏亚雷斯的“性格与力量<ref>{{cite web|title=Barcelona claim Suarez is 'humble'|url=http://www.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/320565.html|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|accessdate=2014-07-12|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714134117/http://www.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/320565.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Luis Suarez: Barcelona will meet Liverpool striker's release clause|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28112887|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2014-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711130322/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28112887|archivedate=2014-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>”。

