===俄罗斯 v. 阿尔及利亚：球迷激光笔助破俄罗斯大门===
{{nft|俄罗斯}}在6月26日对阵{{nft|阿尔及利亚}}的[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週H组#阿尔及利亚_v._俄罗斯|H组决赛]]中1比1战平，阿尔及利亚最终淘汰俄罗斯，进军[[2014年世界杯足球赛淘汰赛阶段|淘汰赛]]。然而俄罗斯队的出线是可预见的，开赛仅六分钟，前锋[[亚历山大·科科林|亚历山大·-{zh-hans:科科林;zh-hk:高哥連;zh-tw:科科林;}-]]就将比分改写成1比0。奇怪的事在第60分钟发生。由[[激光笔|激光笔]]发出的运动绿光，照在了俄罗斯门将[[伊戈爾·阿金費耶夫|-{zh-hans:阿金费耶夫;zh-hk:艾堅菲夫;zh-tw:阿金費耶夫;}-]]的脸上。当时他正防守阿尔及利亚前锋[[伊斯兰·斯利曼尼|-{zh-hans:斯利曼尼;zh-hk:施利文尼}-]]的任意球。俄罗斯主帅[[法比奥·卡佩罗|法比奥·卡佩罗]]指责激光笔引发致命性的失球，他表示：“守门员没法专下心来，激光就照在他脸上。这不是借口，你可以在镜头上看到。”<ref>{{cite news |last=Lowe |first=Sid |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/26/algeria-russia-world-cup-2014-group-h-match-report |title=Algeria 1-1 Russia; World Cup 2014 Group H match report |newspaper=[[卫报|卫报]] |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2014-06-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627002416/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/26/algeria-russia-world-cup-2014-group-h-match-report |archivedate=2014-06-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=World Cup 2014: Fabio Capello unhappy at laser shone at keeper|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28051540|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|accessdate=2014-06-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627192142/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28051540|archivedate=2014-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

赛后，因阿尔及利亚球迷违反了使用激光笔等球场规则，国际足联处以[[阿尔及利亚足球协会|阿尔及利亚足球协会]]5万[[瑞士法郎|瑞士法郎]]罚款，折合美金56200元<ref name="AFF fined">{{cite news|first=Simon|last=Evans|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/06/30/us-soccer-world-alg-lasers-fifa-idINKBN0F52E220140630|title=Algeria zapped with FIFA fine over lasers|publisher=Reuters|date=2014-07-01|accessdate=2014-07-02|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185323/http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/06/30/us-soccer-world-alg-lasers-fifa-idINKBN0F52E220140630|dead-url=no}}</ref>。按照国际足联的《体育场及安保条例》，激光笔在体育场属违禁物品<ref name="FIFA Stadium Safety and Security Regulations">{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/mm/document/tournament/competition/51/53/98/safetyregulations_e.pdf |title=FIFA Stadium Safety and Security Regulations |page=96, "g" |format=PDF |accessdate=2014-07-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101064105/http://www.fifa.com/mm/document/tournament/competition/51/53/98/safetyregulations_e.pdf |archivedate=2013-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

==淘汰赛==
===巴西 v. 智利===
在{{nft|智利}}和{{nft|巴西}}之间展开的[[2014年世界杯足球赛淘汰赛阶段#十六强|首轮淘汰赛]]，存在混乱和争议<ref>{{cite news |title=Brazil vs Chile: as it happened |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10928638/Brazil-vs-Chile-World-Cup-2014-live.html |author=Huw Turbervill |date=2014-06-28 |accessdate=2014-06-28 |publisher=每日电讯报 |archive-date=2014-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628201642/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10928638/Brazil-vs-Chile-World-Cup-2014-live.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

本场比赛的首个进球，被认为是智利后卫[[贡萨洛·哈拉|-{zh-hans:贡萨洛·哈拉;zh-hk:干沙路·查拉}-]]的[[乌龙球|乌龙球]]，但国际足联证实此球是巴西的[[大卫·路易斯|大卫·路易斯]]射入的<ref>{{cite news|title=FIFA confirms Brazil’s goal vs. Chile in Round of 16 was scored by David Luiz, not ruled an own goal by Gonzalo Jara|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/soccer/fifa-confirms-brazil-goal-scored-david-luiz-article-1.1848397|date=2014-06-29|accessdate=2014-06-29|agency=美联社|publisher=NYDailyNews.com|archive-date=2014-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711073932/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/soccer/fifa-confirms-brazil-goal-scored-david-luiz-article-1.1848397|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

英国裁判[[霍华德·韦伯|霍华德·韦伯]]的判罚被批过于苛刻，尤其是针对巴西。[[BBC体育|BBC体育]]评论员，前英格兰前锋[[加里·莱因克尔|加里·莱因克尔]]在视频中表示，韦伯做出一些“玄乎的判罚”，如第13分钟拒绝授予巴西前锋[[浩克_(足球运动员)|-{zh-hans:浩克;zh-hk:侯克;zh-tw:浩克;}-]]点球机会，并在第55分钟有点苛刻地判罚同一球员[[手球|手球]]<ref>{{cite news|title=BBC Sport - World Cup 2014: Brazil had to stay in tournament - Gary Lineker|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28075954|date=2014-06-29|accessdate=2014-06-29|publisher=bbc.com|archive-date=2014-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629231428/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28075954|dead-url=no}}</ref>。-{zh-hans:浩克;zh-hk:侯克;zh-tw:浩克;}-已将球射进智利的大门，但裁判裁定该枚进球由手臂控制而被判无效，对-{zh-hans:浩克;zh-hk:侯克;zh-tw:浩克;}-出示黄牌。包括前英格兰足球运动员[[迈克尔·欧文|-{zh-hans:欧文;zh-hk:奧雲;zh-tw:歐文;}-]]（通过Twitter<ref>{{cite web |title=Huge decision from Howard Webb to give handball against Hulk. I reckon he's got that one wrong |url=https://twitter.com/themichaelowen/status/482936103918641153 |author=迈克尔·欧文 |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715001005/https://twitter.com/themichaelowen/status/482936103918641153 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）在内的其他评论家，亦质疑对-{zh-hans:浩克;zh-hk:侯克;zh-tw:浩克;}-手球的判罚可能过于苛刻<ref>{{cite news |title=Controversial handball call takes a goal away from Brazil - USA Today |author=Nick Schwartz |date=2014-06-28 |url=http://ftw.usatoday.com/2014/06/brazil-chile-handball-hulk-howard-webb/ |publisher=[[今日美国|今日美国]] |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archive-date=2014-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913053606/http://ftw.usatoday.com/2014/06/brazil-chile-handball-hulk-howard-webb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===荷兰 v. 墨西哥===
[[File:Arjen_Robben_20120609.jpg|thumb]]
{{nft|墨西哥}}对阵{{nft|荷兰}}的[[2014年世界杯足球赛淘汰赛阶段#十六强|十六强赛]]经过90分钟，比分1-1。6分钟补时期间，荷兰边锋[[阿尔扬·罗本|-{zh-hans:阿尔扬·罗本;zh-hk:阿揚·洛賓;zh-tw:阿揚·羅本;}-]]被墨西哥后卫[[拉法埃尔·马克斯|-{zh-hans:拉法埃尔·马克斯;zh-hk:拉菲爾·馬基斯;zh-tw:拉菲爾·馬奎斯;}-]]踢倒而被判犯规，随后荷兰点球射手[[克拉斯-扬·亨特拉尔|-{zh-hans:克拉斯-扬·亨特拉尔;zh-hant:克拉斯-揚·亨特拉爾;zh-hk:卡拿斯-恩·亨特拉爾;zh-tw:克拉斯-揚·亨特拉爾;zh-mo:卡拿斯-恩·亨特拉爾;}-]]一记绝杀进球，将比分定格在2-1，从而淘汰墨西哥。罗本因使用[[假摔|假摔]]来赚取点球机会<ref>{{cite news |last=Corder |first=Mike |title=Robben Falls Theatrically to Earn Decisive Penalty |newspaper=ABC News and Associated Press |location=USA |publisher=abcnews.go.com |date=2014-06-29 |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/robben-falls-theatrically-earn-decisive-penalty-24356894 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630083038/http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/robben-falls-theatrically-earn-decisive-penalty-24356894 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Poll |first=Graham |title=Referee Pedro Proenca fell for Arjen Robben's theatrical dive ... |newspaper=The Daily Mail Online |location=United Kingdom |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2014-06-29 |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2674147/Referee-Pedro-Proenca-fell-Arjen-Robbens-theatrical-dive-sides-half-penalties.html |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archive-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630120104/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2674147/Referee-Pedro-Proenca-fell-Arjen-Robbens-theatrical-dive-sides-half-penalties.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Borden |first=Sam |title=Dutch Mount Dramatic Rally With Theatrical Fall |newspaper=New York Times Online |location=New York, USA |publisher=nytimes.com |date=2014-06-29 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/30/sports/worldcup/world-cup-2014-netherlands-tops-mexico-with-2-goals-in-final-minutes.html?_r=0 |accessdate=2014-06-29 |archive-date=2014-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707080705/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/30/sports/worldcup/world-cup-2014-netherlands-tops-mexico-with-2-goals-in-final-minutes.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Kane |first=Desmond |title=Shameful Robben might just cheat his way to World Cup glory |newspaper=Yahoo Eurosport UK |location=UK and Ireland |publisher=Yahoo Eurosport |date=2014-06-29 |url=https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/blogs/desmond-kane/robben-diving-shameful-could-hold-key-dutch-glory-203628281.html |accessdate=2014-06-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714233134/https://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/blogs/desmond-kane/robben-diving-shameful-could-hold-key-dutch-glory-203628281.html |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref>遭到记者广泛谴责而出名<ref>{{cite news |last=Pickup |first=Oliver |title=Arjen Robben joins list of top 9 football divers of all time, but where does he rank compared to the others? |newspaper=The Telegraph Online |location=United Kingdom |publisher=Telegraph.co.uk |date=2014-06-30 |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10935074/Arjen-Robben-joins-list-of-top-9-football-divers-of-all-time-but-where-does-he-rank-compared-to-the-others.html |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archive-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630150534/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup/10935074/Arjen-Robben-joins-list-of-top-9-football-divers-of-all-time-but-where-does-he-rank-compared-to-the-others.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Mokbel |first=Sami |title=Arjen Robben is a diving cheat ... |newspaper=The Daily Mail Online |location=United Kingdom |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2014-06-30 |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2675374/Arjen-Robben-cheat-thats-former-Chelsea-winger-never-return-Premier-League.html |accessdate=2014-06-30 |archive-date=2014-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701073206/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2675374/Arjen-Robben-cheat-thats-former-Chelsea-winger-never-return-Premier-League.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。赛后，墨西哥主帅[[米格尔·埃雷拉|米格尔·埃雷拉]]与葡萄牙裁判[[佩德罗·普罗恩卡|佩德罗·普罗恩卡]]发生口角，他随后在采访时表示：“这是一届所有人针对墨西哥的世界杯<ref>{{cite news|title=Miguel Herrera blasts refs after Mexico World Cup exit|url=http://fansided.com/2014/06/29/miguel-herrera-blasts-refs-mexico-world-cup-exit/#!52Po5|accessdate=2014-06-29|agency=Fansided|publisher=Josh Sanchez|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709195127/http://fansided.com/2014/06/29/miguel-herrera-blasts-refs-mexico-world-cup-exit/#!52Po5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”随后他又在新闻发布会上详细阐述：“四场比赛里，我们有三个灾难性的判罚，这是最糟糕的。罗本三次为搏点球假摔，这不得不要警醒他。如果你对这种作弊的家伙予以处罚，那他就不敢再耍花招了<ref name="Robben admits Daily Mail">{{cite news|title=Arjen Robben admits diving for a penalty... but not for the injury-time spot-kick that put Holland through to the quarter-finals|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2674266/Arjen-Robben-admits-diving-penalty-not-injury-time-spot-kick-Holland-quarter-finals.html|accessdate=2014-06-29|agency=Mail Online|publisher=Mike Dawes|archive-date=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630084528/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2674266/Arjen-Robben-admits-diving-penalty-not-injury-time-spot-kick-Holland-quarter-finals.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”罗本赛后承认比赛期间倒地太明显，并为此道歉：“有一次（最终变成）点球，对方进入禁区，我就轻易地摔倒，我不应该那样。”罗本也表示，上半场有两个禁区内犯规针对他<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nos.nl/wk2014/artikel/668577-robben-bevestigt-was-penalty.html |title=Robben bevestigt: was penalty - NOS Wereldkampioenschap Voetbal |publisher=Nos.nl |date= |accessdate=2014-07-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714232821/http://nos.nl/wk2014/artikel/668577-robben-bevestigt-was-penalty.html |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref><ref name="Robben admits Daily Mail"/>，应当得到罚球。但照马尔克斯所述，罗本在赛后供认“补时的那个不是点球，但之前的是”，这违背了他在发布会上的发言<ref>{{cite news|title=Soccer-Robben confessed penalty unfair, says Mexico captain|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/news/soccer-robben-confessed-penalty-unfair-says-mexico-captain-223112758--sow.html|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715010503/https://sports.yahoo.com/news/soccer-robben-confessed-penalty-unfair-says-mexico-captain-223112758--sow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。荷兰足球协会（[[KNVB|KNVB]]）认为罗本说的话被错误翻译。

===法国 v. 尼日利亚===
{{nft|法国}}和{{nft|尼日利亚}}的十六强比赛后，尼日利亚中场知名球员[[奥格尼·奥纳奇|-{zh-hans:奥格尼·奥纳奇;zh-hk:奧根耶·奧拿斯;}-]]和[[米克尔·约翰|-{zh-hans:米克尔·约翰;zh-hk:約翰·米基爾;zh-tw:米克爾·約翰;}-]]、前锋[[彼得·奥代姆温吉|彼得·奥代姆温吉]]、教练[[斯蒂芬·德克士|斯蒂芬·德克士]]等人，指控美国裁判[[马克·基格|马克·基格]]偏向法国。盖格在比赛中的多个判罚亦被批评，包括：因越位取消尼日利亚前锋[[艾曼纽·艾文历基|艾曼纽·艾文历基]]的进球（尽管回放录像显示该裁决可能正确）；没有就法国前锋[[奥利弗·吉鲁|-{zh-cn:奥利韦尔·吉鲁;zh-hk:奧利華·基奧特;zh-tw:奧利弗·吉魯;}-]]明显肘击尼日利亚中场[[米克尔·约翰|-{zh-hans:米克尔;zh-hk:米基爾;zh-tw:米克爾;}-]]罚出红牌；法国左后卫在角球期间抓住-{zh-hans:奥代姆温吉; zh-hk:奧丹維治;}-，因裁判持续的粗心没有判罚。最值得注意的是，法国中场[[布莱瑟·马图伊迪|-{zh-hans:布莱瑟·马图伊迪;zh-hk:布萊瑟·馬度迪;}-]]蹬踏-{zh-hans:奥纳奇;zh-hk:奧拿斯;}-，导致其左腿肌腱撕裂（需要手术）并-{zh-hans:奥纳奇;zh-hk:奧拿斯;}-被迫由中场[[鲁本·加布里埃尔|鲁本·-{zh-hans:加布里埃尔;zh-hk:加比爾;}-]]换下，却只吃了一张黄牌<ref>{{cite news|title=ONAZI: MATUIDI'S TACKLE WORSE THAN SAUREZ BITE|url=http://africanfootball.com/news/436243/Onazi-Matuidi-s-tackle-worse-than-Saurez-bite|accessdate=2014-07-02|agency=AfricanFootball|publisher=Staff Reporter|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709025125/http://africanfootball.com/news/436243/Onazi-Matuidi-s-tackle-worse-than-Saurez-bite|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Mikel: Giroud meant to elbow me|url=http://www.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/320449.html|accessdate=2014-07-02|agency=ESPN|publisher=ESPN Staff|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714165925/http://www.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/320449.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有评论家指出，该判罚严重影响比赛，尤其是-{zh-hans:奥纳奇;zh-hk:奧拿斯;}-被强制换下，改变了比赛的局面，令尼日利亚丧失最具影响力的中场球员<ref>{{cite news|title=Scouting Report: Should Arsenal Sign Ogenyi Onazi in the Summer Transfer Window?|url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2115432-scouting-report-should-arsenal-sign-ogenyi-onazi-in-the-summer-transfer-window?search_query=onazil|accessdate=2014-07-02|agency=Bleacherreport|publisher=Allan Jiang|archive-date=2014-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718225617/http://bleacherreport.com/articles/2115432-scouting-report-should-arsenal-sign-ogenyi-onazi-in-the-summer-transfer-window?search_query=onazil|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Soccer-Onazi injury allows France to break through to last eight|url=http://news.yahoo.com/soccer-onazi-injury-allows-france-break-last-eight-193401120--sow.html|date=2014-06-30|accessdate=2014-07-02|agency=[[路透社|路透社]]|last=Johnston|first=Patrick|publisher=[[雅虎新闻|雅虎新闻]]|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714175421/http://news.yahoo.com/soccer-onazi-injury-allows-france-break-last-eight-193401120--sow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===巴西 v. 哥伦比亚===
{{Quote box|quote=“我认为他们对裁判已作出很大的抉择，尤其是在哥伦比亚有赢得比赛的机会的关键时刻。[[大卫·路易斯|大卫·路易斯]]意图用六次犯规伤害[[哈梅斯·罗德里格斯|-{zh-cn:哈梅斯·罗德里格斯;zh-hk:占士·洛迪古斯;zh-tw:哈梅斯·羅德里奎茲;}-]]，但裁判从未投出一张卡。这是过去十年里我所见过的最差裁判······当我看到国际足联因这样一场伟大的比赛，祝贺主裁判，我问自己，‘搞什么鬼？他们看的是哪场比赛？’，他们可能误认为这是场棒球或斗牛比赛，根本没看吧<ref name="#1">{{cite web |last=Lopez |first=Amy |url=http://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-dirty-tackle/maradona-angry-at-officials-in-brazil-colombia-game-171038640.html |title=Maradona angry at officials in Brazil-Colombia game | Dirty Tackle - Yahoo Sports |publisher=Sports.yahoo.com |date=2014-07-05 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719162219/http://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/soccer-dirty-tackle/maradona-angry-at-officials-in-brazil-colombia-game-171038640.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”
::——马拉多纳对巴西-哥伦比亚的比赛的评价
|align = right|quoted = 1| width = 33%}}
{{nft|巴西}}和{{nft|哥伦比亚}}的四分之一决赛，刷新了世界杯赛的单场犯规记录（巴西31次，哥伦比亚23次，共54次，只有4张黄牌），包括哥伦比亚后卫[[胡安·卡米洛·苏尼加|胡安·卡米洛·苏尼加]]第88分钟时膝撞巴西前锋[[内马尔|内马尔]]背部，导致内马尔在比赛中被抬走，却连普通犯规都没有吹。随后医疗评估显示内马尔椎骨骨折，无缘剩余比赛<ref name="Neymar out for the tournament">{{cite news |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2014/neymar-out-world-cup-fractured-3813866 |title=Neymar OUT of the World Cup with a 'fractured vertebrae' suffered in quarter-final win over Colombia |newspaper=[[每日镜报|每日镜报]] |last=Daly |first=Jim |date=2014-07-04 |accessdate=2014-07-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705095855/http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2014/neymar-out-world-cup-fractured-3813866 |archivedate=2014-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。哥伦比亚最终以2-1输掉比赛。比赛后，苏尼加坚称他并非故意伤害内马尔<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28173132 |title=Neymar: Injured Brazil forward ruled out of World Cup |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2014-06-04 |accessdate=2014-06-04 |archive-date=2014-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705001328/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/28173132 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://esportes.estadao.com.br/noticias/futebol,zuniga-diz-que-nao-tinha-a-intencao-de-machucar-neymar,1523807 |title=Zúñiga diz que não tinha a intenção de machucar Neymar |publisher=Estadão |date=2014-06-04 |accessdate=2014-06-04 |language=pt |archive-date=2014-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707222359/http://esportes.estadao.com.br/noticias/futebol,zuniga-diz-que-nao-tinha-a-intencao-de-machucar-neymar,1523807 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。内马尔的队友[[蒂亚戈·席尔瓦|-{zh-hans:蒂亚戈·席尔瓦;zh-hk:泰亞高·施華;zh-tw:蒂亞戈·席爾瓦;}-]]为苏尼加辩护，称他不是那种故意造成人身伤害类型的球员<ref>{{cite web |url=http://espndeportes.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/2127522/thiago-silva-defendio-a-zuniga-y-quiere-ganar-la-copa-por-neymar |title=Thiago Silva defendió a Zuñiga y quiere ganar la Copa por Neymar - Futbol - ESPN: Deportes |publisher=Espndeportes.espn.go.com |date=2008-01-01 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714223343/http://espndeportes.espn.go.com/news/story/_/id/2127522/thiago-silva-defendio-a-zuniga-y-quiere-ganar-la-copa-por-neymar |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月5日，据透露，苏尼加曾向内马尔致信道歉，对无意造成的伤害“深感惋惜和难过”<ref>{{cite news|title=Zuniga apologizes to Neymar for tackle|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/dcunited/zuniga-apologizes-to-neymar-for-tackle/2014/07/05/e1a8bec0-0470-11e4-ae91-d5e5645b17c1_story.html|agency=Associated Press|accessdate=6 July 2014|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140707130801/http://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/dcunited/zuniga-apologizes-to-neymar-for-tackle/2014/07/05/e1a8bec0-0470-11e4-ae91-d5e5645b17c1_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

众多媒体及足坛人物（[[马拉多纳|马拉多纳]]等），批评国际足联和西班牙裁判[[卡洛斯·韦拉斯科·卡巴洛|卡洛斯·韦拉斯科·卡巴洛]]偏袒巴西，吹掉哥伦比亚后卫[[马里奥·耶佩斯|-{zh-hans:马里奥·耶佩斯;zh-hk:馬里奧·耶比斯;zh-tw:馬里奧·耶佩斯;}-]]的进球<ref>{{cite web|last1=Worswick|first1=Carl|title=Referee not the determining factor in Colombia defeat|url=http://www.espnfc.com/team/colombia/208/blog/post/1934244/worswick-ref-not-decisive-factor-in-colombia-loss|website=espnfc.com|publisher=ESPN|accessdate=2014-07-12|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185545/http://www.espnfc.com/team/colombia/208/blog/post/1934244/worswick-ref-not-decisive-factor-in-colombia-loss|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不判罚巴西的大量犯规，使得哥伦比亚也变得带有进攻性<ref>{{cite web|title=Brazil v Colombia referee: I am not allowed to discuss decisions|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/05/brazil-colombia-world-cup-referee|website=theguardian.com|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=12 July 2014|archive-date=2014-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140901175930/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/05/brazil-colombia-world-cup-referee|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Burrows |first=Ben |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2014/world-cup-2014-james-rodriguez-3816818 |title=World Cup 2014: James Rodriguez slams referee Carlos Velasco Carballo as Colombia bow out to Brazil - Mirror Online |publisher=Mirror.co.uk |date=2014-07-05 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714184410/http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/world-cup-2014/world-cup-2014-james-rodriguez-3816818 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite web |author=Scott Murray |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/04/brazil-v-colombia-world-cup-2014-quarter-final-live |title=Brazil v Colombia: World Cup 2014 quarter-final – as it happened | Scott Murray | Football |publisher=theguardian.com |date=2014-07-04 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715003226/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jul/04/brazil-v-colombia-world-cup-2014-quarter-final-live |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ripley |first=Dan |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2677300/Brazil-vs-Colombia-World-Cup-2014-LIVE-Follow-quarter-final-action-happens.html |title=Brazil 2-1 Colombia World Cup 2014 MATCH REPORT: David Luiz and Thiago Silva help fire host nation into semi-finals | Mail Online |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2014-07-04 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705103012/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/worldcup2014/article-2677300/Brazil-vs-Colombia-World-Cup-2014-LIVE-Follow-quarter-final-action-happens.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有人更认为，如果卡巴洛当时能妥善控制比赛，这些过多的犯规（尤其是内马尔的受伤）就不会发生<ref>{{cite web |author=Simon Rice |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/worldcup/neymar-out-revealed--fifa-selected-lenient-referees-for-quarterfinals-9586697.html |title=Neymar out: REVEALED - Fifa selected lenient referees for quarter-finals - World Cup 2014 - Football |publisher=The Independent |date=2014-07-05 |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714191331/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/worldcup/neymar-out-revealed--fifa-selected-lenient-referees-for-quarterfinals-9586697.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而FIFA之後亦離奇地沒有再追究苏尼加弄傷内马尔的事故。

===巴西 v. 荷兰===
季军战第二分钟，[[蒂亚戈·席尔瓦|-{zh-hans:蒂亚戈·席尔瓦;zh-hk:泰亞高·施華;zh-tw:蒂亞戈·席爾瓦;}-]]在[[朱利奥·塞萨尔|-{zh-hans:朱利奥·塞萨尔;zh-hk:祖利奧·施薩;zh-tw:儒利奧·塞薩爾;}-]]开球时冲进禁区抢球，并拉倒[[阿尔扬·罗本|-{zh-hans:阿尔扬·罗本;zh-hk:阿揚·洛賓;zh-tw:阿揚·羅本;}-]]。由於羅本正進行[[單刀|單刀]]，按照国际足联规定，席尔瓦应被直接出示红牌驅逐離場，但阿尔及利亚裁判[[贾迈勒·夏伊摩迪|贾迈勒·夏伊摩迪]]仅出示黄牌，與此同時卻對這項於禁区外發生的犯规作出十二碼判罚，最终[[范佩西|范佩西]]破门。荷兰在第16分钟的第二个进球实为[[越位|越位]]，但被裁判忽略。第67分钟，巴西中场[[奥斯卡_(球员)|奥斯卡]]因本场比赛唯一一次假摔而吃黄牌；但回放显示，他是被对手[[戴利·布林德|戴利·-{zh-hans:布林德; zh-hk:白蘭特; zh-hant:布林德;}-]]在禁区内推倒的。戴利因伤离场，进一步证实了两名球員间有大的肢体接触<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espnfc.us/fifa-world-cup/match/383240/brazil-netherlands/report |title=Brazil 0-3 Netherlands - Dutch beat hosts to claim third place at World Cup - ESPN FC |publisher=Espnfc.us |date= |accessdate=2014-07-20 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715132758/http://www.espnfc.us/fifa-world-cup/match/383240/brazil-netherlands/report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==安全问题==
===场馆内===
====建设====
场馆建设受到意外事故、预算超支、工期延误的困扰。建设12个世界杯赛场的事故，牺牲了8名工人。2013年10月下旬，[[马托格罗索州|马托格罗索州]]州长警告[[潘特纳尔体育场|潘特纳尔体育场]]不能100%按照工期完成24小时后，施工时就发生火灾。影片显示，[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週F组#阿根廷_v_波黑|波黑对阵阿根廷开赛前]]。有球迷攀爬用脚手架做成的不稳定楼梯通往场内<ref>{{Citation | url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/18/world-cup-2014-chile-fans-maracana-spain | last=Wilson | first=Jonathan | title=World Cup 2014: Chile fans invade Maracanã before Spain game | newspaper=卫报 | date=2014-06-18 | accessdate=2014-07-17 | archive-date=2014-07-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714230427/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/18/world-cup-2014-chile-fans-maracana-spain | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-18/world-cup-chile-fans-storm-rio-stadium-ahead-of-spain-game.html|title=World Cup Chile Fans Storm Rio Stadium And 85 Detained|accessdate=2014-07-17|archive-date=2014-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712085842/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-18/world-cup-chile-fans-storm-rio-stadium-ahead-of-spain-game.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====无票智利球迷冲击体育馆====
6月18日[[智利国家足球队|智利]]对阵[[西班牙国家足球队|西班牙]]的[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週B组|B组]]比赛中，100名聚集在[[马拉卡纳体育场|马拉卡纳体育场]]外智利球迷强行进入体育场。他们首先突破安检，让一位球迷装病引开保安，随后进入媒体中心把玻璃窗砸碎、挡板推翻，从而进入体育场。据宪兵报道，共有85名球迷被捕，其他人已抵达看台。早前的6月15日[[阿根廷国家足球队|阿根廷]]对阵[[波斯尼亚和黑塞哥维那国家足球队|波黑]]的[[2014年世界杯足球赛决赛週F组|比赛]]中，亦有20名阿根廷球迷做出类似行为<ref>{{Citation | url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/18/world-cup-2014-chile-fans-maracana-spain | last=Wilson | first=Jonathan | title=World Cup 2014: Chile fans invade Maracanã before Spain game | newspaper=The Guardian | date=18 June 2014 | accessdate=2014-07-17 | archive-date=2014-07-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714230427/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/jun/18/world-cup-2014-chile-fans-maracana-spain | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#2"/>。

====英格兰球迷全武行====
据英国警方报道，6月19日[[英格兰国家足球队|英国]]在[[圣保罗|圣保罗]]对阵[[乌拉圭国家足球队|乌拉圭]]的比赛中，两名英国球迷互殴，其中一名的耳朵被咬。遭攻击的球迷提出投诉后，巴西警方着手调查，但无法确认攻击者。英格兰前锋[[斯坦·科利莫尔|斯坦·科利莫尔]]在推特上证实了该事件。首席警察协会发表声明，根据科利莫尔的推文，南约克郡总警司雷切尔·巴特表示：“我们一直努力确认犯罪嫌疑人，力求将他在英国绳之于法，如果可能的话，可将他送回犯下罪行的巴西<ref>{{cite news|title=England fan has piece of ear 'bitten off' at World Cup|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-28072902|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=29 June 2014|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701064803/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-28072902|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

===场馆外===
====单轨铁路垮塌====
6月9日，世界杯开赛前三天，[[圣保罗地铁|圣保罗地铁]]17号线施工过程中，一条水泥支撑梁倒塌，1名工人死亡，另有两人受伤<ref name="Monorail collapses BBC">{{cite news|title=Fatal accident on flagship Sao Paulo monorail|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-27774337|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=9 June 2014|accessdate=2014-07-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704090344/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-27774337|archivedate=2014-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该线建成后，将连接单轨铁路网另外三条前往[[圣保罗国际机场|圣保罗国际机场]]的线路，预计在比赛开始前完成，但施工因未得到环保部门批准而被推迟，预计于2015年下半年完成<ref name="Monorail collapses O Globo">{{cite news|title=Parte de estrutura do monotrilho cai e deixa um morto na Zona Sul de SP|url=http://oglobo.globo.com/brasil/parte-de-estrutura-do-monotrilho-cai-deixa-um-morto-na-zona-sul-de-sp-12778959|work=O Globo|language=pt|date=2014-06-09|accessdate=2014-07-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611091817/http://oglobo.globo.com/brasil/parte-de-estrutura-do-monotrilho-cai-deixa-um-morto-na-zona-sul-de-sp-12778959|archivedate=2014-06-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Monorail collapses Business Insider">{{cite news|title=One Dead After Part Of Unfinished Monorail Being Built For World Cup Collapses In São Paulo|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/sao-paulo-monorail-collapses-one-dead-2014-6|last=Manfred|first=Tony|publisher=Business Insider|date=2014-06-10|accessdate=2014-07-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610184430/http://www.businessinsider.com/sao-paulo-monorail-collapses-one-dead-2014-6|archivedate=2014-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====桥梁垮塌====
7月3日，[[贝洛奥里藏特|贝洛奥里藏特]]一处属于世界杯基建项目的[[立交桥|立交桥]]，施工时坍塌，瓦砾掉落到下方繁忙的车道，2人死亡，22人受伤。一名目击者指责赶工期的当局和企业处理这场灾难的表现“无能<ref name="Overpass collapses BBC">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-28155216 |title=Flyover collapses in Brazil World Cup host city |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2014-07-04 |accessdate=2014-07-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705021338/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-28155216 |archivedate=2014-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Overpass collapses Reuters">{{cite news |title=Overpass collapses in World Cup city, crushes vehicles |agency=[[路透社|路透社]] |date=2014-07-03 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/03/us-brazil-worldcup-accident-idUSKBN0F82A220140703 |last=Cawthorne |first=Andrew |accessdate=2014-07-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705040415/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/03/us-brazil-worldcup-accident-idUSKBN0F82A220140703 |archivedate=2014-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”。

==== 头部受伤救护 ====
比赛中处理头部受伤球员的方式让国际足联饱受批评。两起事故尤其让人关注，一是小组赛阶段比赛中，{{nft|乌拉圭}}后卫[[阿尔瓦罗·佩雷拉|阿尔瓦罗·佩雷拉]]头部受伤后昏倒在地上<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/fifa-world-cup-2014/world-cup-news-2014/alvaro-pereira-knocked-out-then-raring-to-go-20140620-zsfqt.html|title=Alvaro Pereira, knocked out then raring to go|date=2014-06-20|work=[[悉尼先驱晨报|悉尼先驱晨报]]|accessdate=2015-05-09|archive-date=2014-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809121053/http://www.smh.com.au/fifa-world-cup-2014/world-cup-news-2014/alvaro-pereira-knocked-out-then-raring-to-go-20140620-zsfqt.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。乌拉圭队医生暗示将球员替换下场，但他回到了比赛中。这一事件遭到球员工会[[职业球员协会|职业球员协会]]和国际足联执行委员会成员及医务委员会主席米歇尔·德·霍格的批评<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.si.com/soccer/2014/07/13/ap-soc-wcup-final-concussion|title=Kramer head injury revives concussion concern|work=[[体育画报|体育画报]]|date=2014-07-13|accessdate=2015-05-09|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518111636/http://www.si.com/soccer/2014/07/13/ap-soc-wcup-final-concussion|dead-url=no}}</ref>。二是决赛中{{nft|德国}}中场[[克里斯托夫·克拉默|克里斯托夫·克拉默]]在第14分钟的冲撞中头部受创，回到比赛后在第31分钟透支。期间，克拉默迷失方向并糊涂起来，曾一度询问裁判[[尼古拉·里佐利|尼古拉·里佐利]]自己打的是不是世界杯的决赛<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.si.com/planet-futbol/2014/07/17/christoph-kramer-germany-didnt-know-world-cup-final-referee|title=Referee: Christoph Kramer unsure it was World Cup final after head blow|work=[[体育画报|体育画报]]|date=2014-07-17|accessdate=2015-05-09|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155222/http://www.si.com/planet-futbol/2014/07/17/christoph-kramer-germany-didnt-know-world-cup-final-referee|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

